  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that I should be wearing one, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall very exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know-- remember that my parents were, were, were wearing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember very distinctly that when I met some of these children, they start to run after me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were older than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, they cornered me in some place before that I be able to reach back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is where I had the bloody nose and, and black eyes, and some-- lot of blue signs in my back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They accuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I received also in the time very strong warning of my father that I never should leave the area that I supposed to do that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if it wasn't my mother to protect me and with, with tears, perhaps I would be very well beaten by my father with slaps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, what happened after that, I received my good lesson, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this without realizing that I was carrying the lessons of so many Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- of course, I never after that didn't try to make adventure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if something happened, this happened in different ways [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we, at certain point, had to leave the capital on the trains going to our destination to new location outside of the capital in Vidin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My hobby, if I'm able to say that, when I was alone at home was basically to study what my assignment was and to play music, actually.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is when I started very actively as one of my favorite time to spend on my few instruments that I had there and start to compose tunes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I recall in this time also that once my uncle surprised me-- brother, older brother, of my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
